---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="LatentFix | Professional Performance Engineering">
	<div class="fixed inset-0 overflow-hidden pointer-events-none -z-10">
		<div class="absolute -top-[25%] -left-[10%] w-[50%] h-[50%] bg-brand/5 blur-[120px] rounded-full"></div>
	</div>

	<main class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-8">
		<nav class="sticky top-0 z-50 w-full border-b border-white/5 bg-slate-950/80 backdrop-blur-md">
		    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-8 flex justify-between items-center py-5">
		        <a href="/" class="group flex items-center gap-1 transition-transform hover:scale-[1.02]">
		            <div class="text-2xl md:text-4xl font-black tracking-[-0.05em] leading-none">
		                Latent<span class="text-brand">Fix</span>
		            </div>
		        </a>

		        <div class="flex items-center gap-8">
		            <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/vikrambadesara" target="_blank" class="hidden sm:block text-sm font-medium text-text-muted hover:text-white transition-colors">
		                LinkedIn
		            </a>
		            <a href="#audit" class="text-sm font-bold bg-white text-black px-6 py-2.5 rounded-full hover:bg-brand hover:text-white transition-all shadow-xl shadow-brand/5">
		                Free Audit
		            </a>
		        </div>
		    </div>
		</nav>

		<header class="py-24">
		    <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-brand/10 border border-brand/20 text-brand text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mb-6">
		        <span>●</span> Optimized for High-Growth Startups
		    </div>
		    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-semibold tracking-tight leading-[1.1] mb-8">
				Precision performance for <br/> 
				<span class="text-text-muted">modern software stacks.</span>
			</h1>
		    <p class="text-xl text-text-muted max-w-2xl leading-relaxed mb-12">
		        We help engineering teams eliminate bottlenecks across <b>React, React Native, and Node.js</b>. From refactoring <b>heavy Express middleware</b> to <b>optimizing REST API latency</b>, we ensure your infrastructure scales as fast as your user base. ⚡
		    </p>
		    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
		        <a href="#audit" class="bg-white text-black px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg hover:scale-[1.02] transition-transform">Get a Performance Audit</a>
		        <a href="https://wa.me/919499424304" class="group flex items-center justify-center gap-3 border border-white/10 px-8 py-4 rounded-xl font-bold text-lg transition-all hover:border-brand/50 hover:bg-brand/5 hover:text-brand">
		            <span>WhatsApp Vikram</span>
		        </a>
		    </div>
		</header>

		<section class="py-12 overflow-hidden border-y border-white/5 bg-white/[0.01]">
		    <div class="flex whitespace-nowrap gap-12 animate-scroll">
		        <span class="text-xl font-mono text-text-muted/40 uppercase tracking-widest">Node.js</span>
		        <span class="text-xl font-mono text-text-muted/40 uppercase tracking-widest">React</span>
		        <span class="text-xl font-mono text-text-muted/40 uppercase tracking-widest">React Native</span>
		        <span class="text-xl font-mono text-text-muted/40 uppercase tracking-widest">Express</span>
		        <span class="text-xl font-mono text-text-muted/40 uppercase tracking-widest">REST APIs</span>
		        <span class="text-xl font-mono text-text-muted/40 uppercase tracking-widest">PostgreSQL</span>
		        <span class="text-xl font-mono text-text-muted/40 uppercase tracking-widest">Redis</span>
		        <span class="text-xl font-mono text-text-muted/40 uppercase tracking-widest">Analytics Tracking</span>
		        <span class="text-xl font-mono text-text-muted/40 uppercase tracking-widest">Node.js</span>
		        <span class="text-xl font-mono text-text-muted/40 uppercase tracking-widest">React</span>
		        <span class="text-xl font-mono text-text-muted/40 uppercase tracking-widest">React Native</span>
		    </div>
		</section>

		<style>
		    @keyframes scroll {
		        from { transform: translateX(0); }
		        to { transform: translateX(-50%); }
		    }
		    .animate-scroll {
		        animation: scroll 30s linear infinite;
		        width: max-content;
		    }
		</style>

		<section class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 py-24 border-t border-white/5">
		    <div class="group p-8 rounded-2xl hover:bg-white/[0.02] transition-colors">
		        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-brand/10 flex items-center justify-center text-brand mb-6">
		            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="m18 16 4-4-4-4"/><path d="m6 8-4 4 4 4"/><path d="m14.5 4-5 16"/></svg>
		        </div>
		        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">API & Backend</h3>
		        <p class="text-white text-xl font-medium mb-4">Express & REST Optimization</p>
		        <p class="text-text-muted">We eliminate <b>event-loop lag, refactor slow middleware, and optimize SQL query execution plans</b> to ensure your backend never stays in the way of growth. 🚀</p>
		    </div>

		    <div class="group p-8 rounded-2xl hover:bg-white/[0.02] transition-colors">
		        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-brand/10 flex items-center justify-center text-brand mb-6">
		            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect width="14" height="20" x="5" y="2" rx="2" ry="2"/><path d="M12 18h.01"/></svg>
		        </div>
		        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Frontend & Mobile</h3>
		        <p class="text-white text-xl font-medium mb-4">React & Native Vitals</p>
		        <p class="text-text-muted">Specialized in <b>React Native bridge optimization</b> and <b>React rendering cycles</b>. We solve "jank" and slow interactions to provide a buttery-smooth native experience. 📲</p>
		    </div>

		    <div class="group p-8 rounded-2xl hover:bg-white/[0.02] transition-colors">
		        <div class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg bg-brand/10 flex items-center justify-center text-brand mb-6">
		            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21.21 15.89A10 10 0 1 1 8 2.83"/><path d="M22 12A10 10 0 0 0 12 2v10z"/></svg>
		        </div>
		        <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-brand uppercase tracking-widest mb-2">Measurement</h3>
		        <p class="text-white text-xl font-medium mb-4">Analytics & Tracking</p>
		        <p class="text-text-muted">Data-driven performance. We implement <b>precision tracking and monitoring (Sentry, PostHog, or custom)</b> to catch silent bottlenecks before your users do. 📉</p>
		    </div>
		</section>

		<section class="py-24 border-y border-white/5">
		    <div class="max-w-3xl">
		        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-8 tracking-tight text-white">Why performance is your secret weapon.</h2>
		        <div class="space-y-8">
		            <div class="flex gap-6">
		                <div class="text-brand font-bold text-2xl italic">01.</div>
		                <div>
		                    <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Higher Conversion</h4>
		                    <p class="text-text-muted">A 100ms delay in response time can drop conversion rates by 7%. Speed isn't just a technical metric; it's a revenue metric.</p>
		                </div>
		            </div>
		            <div class="flex gap-6">
		                <div class="text-brand font-bold text-2xl italic">02.</div>
		                <div>
		                    <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white">Lower Infrastructure Costs</h4>
		                    <p class="text-text-muted">Optimized Express APIs and SQL queries require fewer server resources. We help you scale your user base while keeping your cloud bill flat.</p>
		                </div>
		            </div>
		        </div>
		    </div>
		</section>

		<section class="py-24 border-t border-white/5">
		    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-16 tracking-tight text-center">From Bottleneck to Benchmark in 3 Weeks.</h2>
		    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 text-center">
		        <div class="space-y-4">
		            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand text-black font-bold rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto text-xl shadow-lg shadow-brand/20">1</div>
		            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">The Deep Audit</h4>
		            <p class="text-text-muted text-sm px-4">We hook into your APM tools or logs to identify the exact SQL queries or React components killing your speed.</p>
		        </div>
		        <div class="space-y-4">
		            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand text-black font-bold rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto text-xl shadow-lg shadow-brand/20">2</div>
		            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Surgical Optimization</h4>
		            <p class="text-text-muted text-sm px-4">We don't just give advice; we push PRs. We refactor the critical path, implement caching, and tune your DB.</p>
		        </div>
		        <div class="space-y-4">
		            <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-brand text-black font-bold rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto text-xl shadow-lg shadow-brand/20">3</div>
		            <h4 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Scaling Guardrails</h4>
		            <p class="text-text-muted text-sm px-4">We set up automated performance tests so that your team can keep shipping fast without regressing.</p>
		        </div>
		    </div>
		</section>

		<section class="py-16 border-t border-white/5">
		    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-16 tracking-tight">Proven results in high-stakes environments.</h2>
		    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
		        <div class="p-10 rounded-3xl bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5 hover:border-brand/30 transition-colors">
		            <div class="text-brand font-mono text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-6">Logistics Optimization</div>
		            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 leading-snug">Reduced system-wide latency by 30% for a multi-plant logistics network.</h3>
		            <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Refactored core system architecture to handle real-time fleet availability and order processing across 16 client plants.</p>
		        </div>
		        <div class="p-10 rounded-3xl bg-white/[0.02] border border-white/5 hover:border-brand/30 transition-colors">
		            <div class="text-brand font-mono text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-6">Real-Time Systems</div>
		            <h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-4 leading-snug">Eliminated production environment bottlenecks for engineering teams.</h3>
		            <p class="text-text-muted leading-relaxed">Built high-performance streaming solutions using WebSockets and Node.js to provide instant access to mission-critical production logs.</p>
		        </div>
		    </div>
		</section>

		<section id="audit-intro" class="my-12 p-6 md:p-16 rounded-[2.5rem] bg-surface border border-white/5 text-center">
			<h2 class="text-4xl font-semibold mb-6">Ready to optimize?</h2>
			<p class="text-lg text-text-muted mb-10 max-w-xl mx-auto">Book a 15-minute introductory call. We'll discuss your current challenges and provide immediate actionable feedback.</p>
		</section>

		<section id="audit" class="my-28 p-6 md:p-16 rounded-[2.5rem] bg-surface border border-white/4">
			<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
				<div class="text-center mb-12">
					<h2 class="text-4xl font-semibold mb-4">Request a Performance Audit</h2>
					<p class="text-text-muted">Tell us about your bottlenecks. We'll review your details and reach out within 24 hours to schedule a deep dive.</p>
				</div>

				<form action="https://formspree.io/f/mbdzjvea" method="POST" class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
					<div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
						<label for="full-name" class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-brand">Full Name</label>
						<input type="text" id="full-name" name="Full Name" required placeholder="John Doe" 
							class="bg-black/40 border border-white/10 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 focus:border-brand outline-none transition" />
					</div>
					<div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
						<label for="company" class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-brand">Company / Project</label>
						<input type="text" id="company" name="Company / Project" placeholder="LatentFix" 
							class="bg-black/40 border border-white/10 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 focus:border-brand outline-none transition" />
					</div>

					<div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
						<label for="bottleneck" class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-brand">Primary Bottleneck</label>
						<select id="bottleneck" name="Primary Bottleneck" class="bg-black/40 border border-white/10 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 focus:border-brand outline-none transition appearance-none">
							<option value="API Latency (Slow Responses)">API Latency (Slow Responses)</option>
							<option value="Database Performance (Slow Queries)">Database Performance (Slow Queries)</option>
							<option value="Scaling Issues (Server Crashes)">Scaling Issues (Server Crashes)</option>
							<option value="Frontend Vitals (Speed)">Frontend Vitals (Speed)</option>
							<option value="Analytics / Revenue Tracking">Analytics / Revenue Tracking</option>
							<option value="Other / General Optimization">Other / General Optimization</option>
						</select>
					</div>
					<div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
						<label for="stack" class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-brand">Primary Stack</label>
						<select id="stack" name="Primary Stack" class="bg-black/40 border border-white/10 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 focus:border-brand outline-none transition appearance-none">
							<option value="Node.js / TypeScript">Node.js / TypeScript</option>
							<option value="Nest.js / TypeScript">Nest.js / TypeScript</option>
							<option value="Analytics">Analytics</option>
							<option value="React / React Native">React / React Native</option>
							<option value="SQL (PostgreSQL/MySQL)">SQL (PostgreSQL/MySQL)</option>
							<option value="NoSQL (MongoDB/Redis)">NoSQL (MongoDB/Redis)</option>
							<option value="Other">Other</option>
						</select>
					</div>

					<div class="md:col-span-2 grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
						<div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
							<label for="email" class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-brand">Email Address</label>
							<input type="email" id="email" name="Email Address" placeholder="vikram@latentfix.com" 
								class="bg-black/40 border border-white/10 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 focus:border-brand outline-none transition w-full" />
							<span id="email-error" class="text-[10px] text-red-500 uppercase font-bold tracking-tight hidden">Invalid email format</span>
						</div>
						<div class="flex flex-col gap-2">
							<label for="phone" class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-brand">WhatsApp / Phone</label>
							<input type="tel" id="phone" name="WhatsApp / Phone" placeholder="+91 XXX-XXX-XXXX" 
								class="bg-black/40 border border-white/10 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 focus:border-brand outline-none transition w-full" />
							<span id="phone-error" class="text-[10px] text-red-500 uppercase font-bold tracking-tight hidden">Min 10 digits required</span>
						</div>
					</div>

					<div class="md:col-span-2 flex flex-col gap-2">
						<label for="details" class="text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest text-brand">How can we help?</label>
						<textarea id="details" name="How can we help?" rows="4" placeholder="Describe the issue..." 
							class="bg-black/40 border border-white/10 rounded-xl px-4 py-3 focus:border-brand outline-none transition"></textarea>
					</div>

					<div class="md:col-span-2 mt-4">
						<div id="global-error" class="text-center text-[14px] text-red-500 uppercase font-bold tracking-widest mb-4 hidden">
							Please provide a valid email or phone number to continue.
						</div>
						<button type="submit" 
							class="w-full bg-white text-black font-black py-5 rounded-2xl text-xl hover:bg-brand hover:text-white transition-all shadow-xl shadow-brand/5 cursor-pointer">
							Request Free Audit
						</button>
						<p class="text-center text-[10px] text-text-muted mt-4 uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">Zero Strings Attached. Engineering Focused.</p>
					</div>
				</form>
			</div>
		</section>

		<script is:inline>
			const form = document.querySelector('form');
			const emailInput = document.getElementById('email');
			const phoneInput = document.getElementById('phone');

			const emailError = document.getElementById('email-error');
			const phoneError = document.getElementById('phone-error');
			const globalError = document.getElementById('global-error');

			const emailPattern = /^[^\s@]+@[^\s@]+\.[^\s@]+$/;

			const toggleError = (input, errorEl, isInvalid) => {
				if (isInvalid) {
					input.classList.add('border-red-500');
					input.classList.remove('border-white/10', 'focus:border-brand');
					errorEl?.classList.remove('hidden');
				} else {
					input.classList.remove('border-red-500');
					input.classList.add('border-white/10', 'focus:border-brand');
					errorEl?.classList.add('hidden');
				}
			};

			emailInput.addEventListener('blur', () => {
				const val = emailInput.value.trim();
				toggleError(emailInput, emailError, val !== "" && !emailPattern.test(val));
			});

			phoneInput.addEventListener('input', (e) => {
				e.target.value = e.target.value.replace(/[^0-9+]/g, '');
			});

			phoneInput.addEventListener('blur', () => {
				const val = phoneInput.value.replace(/\D/g, '');
				toggleError(phoneInput, phoneError, phoneInput.value.trim() !== "" && val.length < 10);
			});

			form.addEventListener('submit', (e) => {
				const emailVal = emailInput.value.trim();
				const phoneDigits = phoneInput.value.replace(/\D/g, '');
				
				const isEmailValid = !emailVal || emailPattern.test(emailVal);
				const isPhoneValid = !phoneDigits || phoneDigits.length >= 10;
				const hasContactInfo = emailVal !== "" || phoneDigits !== "";

				// Reset global error
				globalError.classList.add('hidden');

				if (!hasContactInfo) {
					e.preventDefault();
					globalError.classList.remove('hidden');
					emailInput.classList.add('border-red-500');
					phoneInput.classList.add('border-red-500');
					return;
				}

				if (!isEmailValid || !isPhoneValid) {
					e.preventDefault();
					alert('Please fix the highlighted errors before submitting.');
				}
			});
		</script>

		<section class="py-24 border-t border-white/5">
		    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-12 tracking-tight">Immediate Performance Wins ⚡</h2>
		    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
		        <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white/[0.01] border border-white/5">
		            <h4 class="text-brand font-bold mb-2">01. Node.js Event Loop</h4>
		            <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">Avoid heavy computational tasks in your Express routes. Use Worker Threads or offload to a background job to keep the loop free for incoming requests.</p>
		        </div>
		        <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white/[0.01] border border-white/5">
		            <h4 class="text-brand font-bold mb-2">02. React Native "Jank"</h4>
		            <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">Minimize bridge traffic. Keep animations in the native thread and avoid passing huge data blobs between JS and the native side.</p>
		        </div>
		        <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white/[0.01] border border-white/5">
		            <h4 class="text-brand font-bold mb-2">03. SQL Indexing</h4>
		            <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">A missing index on a foreign key can turn a 10ms query into a 2s bottleneck as your table grows. Audit your slow query logs monthly.</p>
		        </div>
		        <div class="p-8 rounded-2xl bg-white/[0.01] border border-white/5">
		            <h4 class="text-brand font-bold mb-2">04. Analytics Payload</h4>
		            <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">Third-party tracking scripts are often the biggest cause of high TBT (Total Blocking Time). Load them via a Web Worker or use a server-side proxy.</p>
		        </div>
		    </div>
		</section>

		<footer class="py-20 border-t border-white/5 flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between text-text-muted text-sm">
			<p>© 2026 LatentFix. Engineering Excellence from Gurugram.</p>
			<div class="flex gap-8 mt-4 md:mt-0">
				<a href="https://linkedin.com/in/vikrambadesara" class="hover:text-white">LinkedIn</a>
				<a href="https://x.com/latentfix" class="hover:text-white">Twitter / X</a>
			</div>
		</footer>
	</main>
</Layout>